high_descs: Turn and walk to the countertop between the fridge and the stove.
Pick up the spatula on the right side of the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the right side of the stove
Place the spatula in the copper pan on the back right burner
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it
Turn around and walk to the round gray table
Place the pan with the spatula in it near the edge of the table at the handle ends of the two spoons
anns.task_desc: Put a spatula in a pan and place them on the table

high_descs: Walk forward and face the counter space next to the stove.
Grab the spatula off of the counter.
Walk right and face the stove.
Place the spatula in the back right pan on the stove.
Grab the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the table in the corner of the room.
Place the pan on the table next to the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right, take a few steps to the counter next to the stove
Take the spatula from the counter
Take a few steps to the right
Put the spatula in the pan on the stove
Take the pan from the stove
Turn around, head to the black kitchen table
Put the pan on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: Put the spatula in the pan, put the pan on the black kitchen table
